SIMPLE: futurity
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Futurity
<hw>Fu*tu"ri*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Futurities</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>State of being that is yet to come; future
state.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Future time; time to come; the future.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Event to come; a future event.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>All <qex>futurities</qex> are naked before the All-seeing Eye.</q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>futurology</ent>⟦br⟧
